headline: Archway Appoints New President of Fund Administration to Support Growth and Client Innovation
summary: Archway Group, a leading provider of technology and outsourced services to single and multi-family offices, today announced the appointment of Megan Greer as President of Fund Administration. In this newly created role, Greer will oversee the strategic direction, operational performance, and continued expansion of Archway's fund administration capabilities for ultra-high-net-worth families, family offices, and private investment partnerships.
